    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? This car is in absolute mint condition and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been my pride and joy, meticulously cared for, and it drives like a total dream. If you're looking for something that's basically brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself\u2014you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 43500.0,
