      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade E46 M3 in pristine condition. This specimen features the high-revving S54 inline-six, boasting a linear power band and individual throttle bodies, recently optimized with a full Vanos bulletproofing and valve clearance adjustment. The drivetrain utilizes the desirable Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission paired with a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis is structurally perfect, with proactive subframe reinforcement and fresh polyurethane bushings ensuring maximum torsional rigidity. Finished in original Carbon Black metallic with zero paint correction required, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector seeking mechanical perfection and documented provenance.",
